    ('cat_doll_soft_toy_care', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for rag doll carry', 'Corolle Rag Doll Blandine Sweet Dreams', 'Corolle', 'Adventure Toys', 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/corolle-rag-doll-blandine-sweet-dreams/', NULL, '£24.99', 'in_stock', 'Birth +', 'A soft rag style Corolle doll for cuddle, carry and simple care, with a floppy body that fits under a toddler arm indoors.', 'Some toddlers prefer a rag flop for dragging from room to room. Blandine keeps Corolle quality while limp limbs make carry simpler on short indoor trips. Choose when Miss Floral already sits on the shelf and you want a different soft care friend.', 'Rag doll carry care.', 'Second Corolle; brand cap full.', 'buy', true, 'Soft character gift.', 'Pick floral OR Blandine, not both unless gifting elsewhere.', 'Supervise.', 'good', ARRAY['adventuretoys.co.uk corolle-rag-doll-blandine']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_doll_soft_toy_care', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for tuck in bed prop', 'Goki Dolls Bed', 'Goki', 'Toytastic', 'https://toytastic.co.uk/product/goki-dolls-bed/', NULL, '£16.99', 'in_stock', '1 year +', 'A wooden dolls bed with a simple mattress space, sized for soft toys and small dolls rather than fashion doll houses.', 'Care play deepens when carry has somewhere to end. This Goki bed makes tuck in the point of the game without needing a full dolls house. Best once a soft doll already lives on the sofa and you want one prop that finishes bedtime copy.', 'Bed prop for care.', 'Needs a soft doll they already own or buy separately.', 'buy', true, 'Pair with soft doll.', 'Skip if a dolls bed already sits in the room.', 'Supervise.', 'good', ARRAY['toytastic.co.uk goki-dolls-bed']::text[], 'none'),
